text: Haultain is a surname, and may refer to: * Arnold Haultain, British writer * Frederick W. Haultain, politician in Canada West * Frederick W. A. G. Haultain, premier of the Canadian Northwest Territories and son of Frederick W. Haultain * H. E. T. Haultain, Canadian engineer and inventor * Lynne Haultain, Australian radio broadcaster * Theodore Haultain, New Zealand politician * Willem Haultain de Zoete, Dutch admiral ==See also== * Haultain, Saskatoon in Canada, named for Frederick W. A. G. Haultain
title: Haultain
